author: hwright
msg: Add an compile-time option to the svn_editor_t callbacks which ensures they
are driven in accordance with the API requirements.
Implement the first set of verification of these requirements, namely that
all incomplete children specified when adding a directory must be later added
(svn_editor_t): Add a couple new members, conditioned on the above macro.
svn_editor_add_absent): Populate and prune the pending children hash.
(svn_editor_complete): Make sure all children have been handled.
